(386, 1, '2016-09-12 11:26:06', '2016-09-12 11:26:06', '[vc_row top=\"60px\" bottom=\"150px\" el_class=\"faq-row\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: 500; text-align: center;\">Frequently asked questions</h3>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_tta_accordion shape=\"square\" color=\"white\" c_icon=\"chevron\" c_position=\"right\" active_section=\"1\" no_fill=\"true\" collapsible_all=\"true\" el_class=\"mnky-accordion\"][vc_tta_section title=\"What is FinTech?\" tab_id=\"1450023211952-3903973f-46c1\"][vc_column_text]FinTech is a job/ partnership advertisement platform for professionals and companies from creative industries such as information technology, graphic design, audiovisual graphics, engineering, marketing and architecture.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Who is this made for?\" tab_id=\"1450023212178-f3e45a46-312d\"][vc_column_text]FinTech is made for companies/ private individuals in need of assistance on their short term/ long term projects as well as for creative professionals seeking new challenges to boost their experience.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"What do you offer?\" tab_id=\"1450025967336-e0850113-e5ef\"][vc_column_text]We provide opportunity for creative folks to find interesting projects in the scope and intensity they wish. On the other hand, companies and private individuals may find the right professionals to fulfill their projects. [/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"What will I gain by having a profile in FinTech?\" tab_id=\"1450263180391-5e79b4ad-0a53\"][vc_column_text]You will establish an online presence and will be able to show your skills and experience to others, which will increase your possibility to receive job/ partnership offers from persons looking for assistance.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Does it matter where I am from?\" tab_id=\"1450026026265-ebd616bf-40f4\"][vc_column_text]No. Geographic location is not an obstacle for creative industries. We offer our service worldwide. Just to note we are based in Europe.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Do I need skills to use the service?\" tab_id=\"1450026085820-4ad6d672-6592\"][vc_column_text]No. FinTech platform is made user-friendly so it is simple and easy to post a job or create a profile. Moreover, FinTech team will provide you any support you need! [/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Why should I join FinTech?\" tab_id=\"1450026159592-76f0cfa8-4ae8\"][vc_column_text]By joining FinTech you will have a chance to contribute to the creative industry. Companies and professionals will be able to interact and by doing that - help each other to reach goals and surpass any limitations.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 style=\"font-weight: 500; text-align: center;\">Have more questions?</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Whether you have a question about our services, need assistance or just want to talk, we want to hear from you.\n<a href=\"#\">Contact our support team.</a></p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Help Center', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'help-center', '', '', '2016-09-12 11:26:06', '2016-09-12 11:26:06', '', 0, 'http://mnkythemes.com/fintechwp/davos/?page_id=386', 0, 'page', '', 0),
