e with our Privacy Policy, you agree that FinTechWP shall be free to use or disseminate a Submission on an unrestricted basis for any purpose. If you submit information to the Site, you grant FinTechWP a non-exclusive, worldwide, royalty-free license to (in any media now known or not currently known or invented) link to, utilize, use, copy, exploit, and prepare derivative works of the Submission. No information you submit shall be deemed confidential. However, FinTechWP agrees to use your information in accordance with FinTechWP’s Privacy Policy applicable to personally identifiable information. You retain ownership of any copyrights or other intellectual property rights applicable to any information you submit to FinTechWP. Notwithstanding the foregoing, you hereby assign to FinTechWP all right, title and interest in and to any new feature that you may suggest or submit to FinTechWP and you acknowledge and agree that FinTechWP may use such suggestion or submission in any manner, including, without limitation, to develop features for the Site.\n\nYou agree that any Submission by you will comply with the “General Use Restrictions” as set forth above. FinTechWP reserves the right (but shall have no obligation) to pre-screen, review, flag, filter, modify, refuse or remove any or all parts of a Submission should it determine that such Submission is in violation with any provision of the Terms.\n<h4><strong>Refund Policy</strong></h4>\nFinding the right candidate may be a timely process, thus it may be not enough with maximum listing period per one job post provided by us (e.g. 30 days) in order to achieve expected results. In case your listing has expired and no one applied for it, thus you were unable to find the right professional – you may apply for a refund or republish you listing one more time completely free. Please note that you may apply for a refund or republish your listing within 30 days after your listing has expired.\n\nIf you still are not satisfied with the results of your listings, please contact our support team at <a href=\"#\">support@fintechwp.eu</a>.\n<h4><strong>Trademarks and Copyrights</strong></h4>\nThe trademarks, service marks, brands, names, logos and designs (“Trademarks”) of FinTechWP or others used on this Site and in the Services are the property of FinTechWP or their respective owners. You may not remove or alter any Trademark. You may not use any trademark displayed on the Site or in the Services without the express prior written permission of FinTechWP or the respective owner, and nothing contained on this Site grants by implication, waiver, estoppel or otherwise, any right to use such trademarks. All of the Materials appearing on this Site and in the Services, including but not limited to, text elements, site design, images and icons, as well as the selection, assembly and arrangement thereof, are the sole property of FinTechWP, Copyright © 2014-2015, unless otherwise specified. All rights not expressly granted herein are reserved. Except as otherwise required by applicable law, any reproduction, distribution, modification, retransmission or publication of any copyrighted material is strictly prohibited without the express written consent of the copyright owner.\n<h4><strong>Indemnification</strong></h4>\nYou agree to defend, indemnify and hold harmless FinTechWP and its affiliates, representatives, partners, agents and employees from and against any and all liabilities, claims, costs and expenses, including attorneys’ fees, that arise out of or in connection with your use of the Site and/or the Services or breach of these Terms.\n<h4><strong>Disclaimer of Warranty</strong></h4>\nYou acknowledge and agree that this site and/or the services are being provided on an “as is” basis without warranty of any kind, express or implied, and may include certain errors, omissions, outdated information which may affect the quality of the materials. You acknowledge that the materials have not been independen