(1299, 1, '2018-05-07 11:01:25', '2018-05-07 11:01:25', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h1><strong><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\">We can make your idea into a reality</span></strong></h1>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"align: justify;\">Project On Wings is a one of a kind platform for sharing projects and innovative ideas directly to the respective technical industry. It aims to connect students with prominent representatives from the companies by providing a channel to upload projects, have them reviewed and put it on their table for a potential to be sold or collaborated with.</span>\n\nProject On Wings acts as a solution platform which gathers real time solutions to the issues posted by the industry. Being in the mold, we understand the difficulties a student have to go through to get his / her idea exposed. It is also extremely difficult to find the right environment for it to be nurtured. On the other hand, the industries have not yet fully tapped the potentials of the young minds but doing which can actually act as a great catalyst for growth.\n\nKeeping these two factors in mind, Project On Wings was carefully fabricated to ensure quality connections on both the sides while maintaining security and economic benefits at its maximum. The list of industries associated with Project On Wings begin from aviation all the way to chemical technologies. As our student base gets more diverse, we procure the interest of more  industries. Our in – house review committee reviews each project uploaded on the site and provides quick feedback and mentoring options. The committee consists of prominent industry leaders and professors working in the finest organizations and colleges in the country.\n\n<strong>In a nutshell, Project On Wings is the house where your ideas and growth are taken seriously and all the tools are provided for it, just for you.</strong>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][mnky_button 