tant;padding-left: 60px !important;background-color: #f2f1ef !important;}\"][mnky_ordered_list number=\"01.\" size=\"ol_large\" last_item=\"last\" number_color=\"#0b3b5b\" divider_color=\"#d6bda0\"][/mnky_ordered_list][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2><b>Register</b></h2>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"15px\"][vc_column_text]Register<strong> </strong>yourself first with Project On Wings by clicking on the Login / Register button on our website.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"55px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1476108288948{padding: 60px !important;background-color: #f8f7f6 !important;}\"][mnky_ordered_list number=\"02.\" size=\"ol_large\" last_item=\"last\" number_color=\"#0b3b5b\" divider_color=\"#d6bda0\"][/mnky_ordered_list][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2><b>Fill</b></h2>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"15px\"][vc_column_text]Fill in details of yourself, upload your photo and complete the details regarding your project according to the layout we specify. Here’s a tip, the more accurate and creative you are with your information, the more are the chances to be instantly recognized![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1476108328451{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-right: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;padding-left: 60px !important;background-color: #f8f7f6 !important;}\"][mnky_ordered_list number=\"03.\" size=\"ol_large\" last_item=\"last\" number_color=\"#0b3b5b\" divider_color=\"#d6bda0\"][/mnky_ordered_list][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2><b>Choose</b></h2>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"15px\"][vc_column_text]Choose<strong> </strong>the most preferred 3 companies you want to pitch your project to. Again, you MUST conduct a comprehensive research on your selections and identify if they are the perfect ones to take your project. If required, you will then be required to digitally sign the NDA and the Terms and Conditions sheet. Also note that, we do not guarantee the nature of responses from the companies but yes, we keep yours on their table.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1476108325283{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-right: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;padding-left: 60px !important;background-color: #f2f1ef !important;}\"][mnky_ordered_list number=\"04.\" size=\"ol_large\" last_item=\"last\" number_color=\"#0b3b5b\" divider_color=\"#d6bda0\"][/mnky_ordered_list][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2><b>Review </b></h2>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"15px\"][vc_column_text]Once the registration is complete and verified, your project would undergo analysis through the <strong>review committee </strong>who will surely have the expertise in the area of your work. If their review is positive, it will be transferred to the company’s end. Otherwise, it will come back to you with a comprehensive feedback. There lies the opportunity to further expand on that and acquire valuable mentoring from the committee and perhaps re-work on the project.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1476108328451{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-right: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;padding-left: 60px !important;background-color: #f8f7f6 !important;}\"][mnky_ordered_list number=\"05.\" size=\"ol_large\" last_item=\"last\" number_color=\"#0b3b5b\" divider_color=\"#d6bda0\"][/mnky_ordered_list][vc_empty_space height=\"30px\"][vc_column_text]\n<h2><b>Updates</b></h2>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"15px\"][vc_column_text]Updates would be shared on the progress and we promise to clear the connection within a time frame. Once the company approves it, you will be connected to them and it is up to you to sell or collaborate![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=\"100px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" disable_element=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1528978957315{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;background-color: #1e2533 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=\"70px\"][mnky_testimonial_slider flex_animation=\"slide\" slide_speed=\"10\"][mnky_testimonial name=\"Adam Love\" author_dec=\"Client\" position=\"Designer\" img_url=\"678\" text_color=\"#96969e\"][vc_column_text]These guys do pretty amazing job. Quality and attention to details in their products is hard to find\nanywhere else. I would definitely recommend to try out one of their products and see it yourself. [/vc_column_text][/mnky_testimonial][mnky_testimonial name=\"Betty Cuda\" author_dec=\"Big Fan\" position=\"Designer\" img_url=\"676\" text_color=\"#96969e\"][vc_column_text]I have found out about this FinTech company only a month ago and I fell in love with their services right away. Can’t wait to see you guys at World FinTech Expo in New York. Cheers![/vc_column_text][/mnky_testimonial][mnky_testimonial name=\"Dee End\" author_dec=\"Supporter\" position=\"Designer\" img_url=\"679\" text_color=\"#96969e\"][vc_column_text]Last few years I was closely following company activities and always trying out their latest products, and needless to say, I was never disappointed. It is nice when company constantly improves.[/vc_column_text][/mnky_testimonial][/mnky_testimonial_slider][vc_empty_space height=\"70px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2018-09-03 03:33:04', '2018-09-03 03:33:04', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/pow/?page_id=1299', 0, 'page', '', 0),
